The '''Iron Throne''' was a mysterious mercantile organization that operated out of the [[Eastern Heartlands]] during the 14{{th}} century [[DR]]. Though it controlled much of the weapons trade across the realms during its time,

While it was a criminal organization in every sense of the word, the Iron Throne thrived in part because of the facade it projected to the rest of [[Faerûn]]: it was an honorable business that served the best interests of the realms. 

{{Quote|''"We shall rule them from an Iron Throne, built of the weapons of our trade..."''|[[Sfena]] in [[1347 DR]]}}
